Users

Volunteer
The person motivated to contribute for the society's good

Problem
I want to discover the volunteer gigs

Solution
A single platform for all upcoming events that will need volunteers. The main dashboard includes a dashboard with dates, vacant positions, qualifications etc. Easy to sign up and get involved. Can gain karma and become a desirable volunteer for future events.

_

Event Manager
Event organiser looking for volunteers for their non-profit event

Problem
How to find volunteers to cater the needs that I can trust?

Solution
A platform that allows to screen and train volunteers outside of regular work hours. Also a database of active volunteers and similar events on the island. A way to start small and grow a movement.
